column2:
"Good work. Your report is excellent.
It looks like you've gotten the hang of the rod."

"You have a solid foundation now, so you can
continue to learn."

"You can keep that rod.
I hope you enjoy it."

"See you later. Don't let me find out
you haven't been practicing with your rod."
"You can now invite Marlu to join you as a partner."

"Joseph has issued a client order.

You can find Joseph in the upper gate area."
